1.title: The Queen Diva Is Back!

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Freedia is shaking things up and letting folks know #everythingmustchange. Freedia's recent felony conviction forces her to change everything in her life and career - from ending a lifelong love of marijuana to figuring out who in her world might be holding her back. Freedia is back and nothing or nobody will stand in her way to reclaim her throne.

2.title: Booty Poppin Potatoes

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: It's the Queen's BIRTHDAY and parole ain't stopping this DIVA from celebrating with family, friends and getting lit. Meanwhile chef Freedia hits the streets to better her community with her famous booty poppin potatoes. While auditions for dancers come to a booty-shaking halt as things get heated with the crew.

3.title: The Power of Weed

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Freedia heads back to Los Angeles to attend the Grammy Awards, but the temptation of weed affects her every step and threatens her ability to stay out of jail. Meanwhile a new crew is coming in and trying to "show out" and the veteran dancers are NOT having it.

4.title: Team Freedia: Veterans vs Rookies

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: While Freedia lives it up in LA, Berto is mixing things up with the dancers in New Orleans and Tootie snaps like an alligator when she hears Freedia is bonding with the new dancers deep in the swamps of Louisiana.

5.title: Girl Down!

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: It's Mardi Gras in New Orleans and Freedia has finally earned a coveted spot in the main parade, but a visit by a mysterious voodoo priest unsettles her as she hears shocking predictions about her future.

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

7.plot: Big Freedia's best friend, Katey Red, heads to the altar while competing LA-based record companies approach Freedia with life-changing opportunities

8.title: Sin City Shakedown

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

8.plot: It's an explosive finale as Big Freedia takes over Las Vegas for a show-stopping performance, only to have drama follow from New Orleans that threatens to ruin Freedia's reputation and show.

1.title: The King and Queen of Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: When Big Freedia's manager suggests teaming up with an internet sensation, Mr. Ghetto, for an international tour, not everyone on Freedia's team agrees this is a good idea, and the collaboration is tested at a local show.

2.title: The Big Break-Up

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Big Freedia's worst suspicions are confirmed when Mr. Ghetto is arrested, jeopardizing the King and Queen of Bounce tour.

3.title: Old School Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Stopping traffic on the streets of New Orleans and dancing on top of cars, Big Freedia goes back to her DIY roots - and risks arrest - to shoot the wildest Bounce video yet.

4.title: Dream Team of Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Old grudges and wounded egos resurface when Big Freedia teams up with fellow Bounce artists to record a Bounce song for kids.

5.title: School House Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: Preparing for the first-ever Bounce show for kids, Big Freedia has to overhaul her act for a young audience and overcome the notion that Bounce is strictly X-rated.

6.title: Power Games

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: On the eve of their first international tour, dissension erupts in Team Freedia when old friends are excluded from the trip to Brazil.

7.title: Heads Will Roll

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

7.plot: When the first show in Brazil proves to be rocky when Renee fills in as DJ, the team has to rebuild their act in time for the big show in Rio.

8.title: World Meets Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

8.plot: Mardi Gras meets Carnival, and Brazilian booty shakes, as Big Freedia kicks off her international tour with the wildest Bounce party ever in Rio de Janeiro.

1.title: Bounce Texas Style

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Freedia prepares for the prestigious South by Southwest Music Festival in Austin, Texas, but with his mother's ailing health and fighting between his two managers, Renee and Melvin, the Queen of Bounce is being pulled in too many directions. The team arrives at the festival only to endure a series of mishaps due to Renee and Melvin's lack of focus, forcing Freedia to re-evaluate his team.

2.title: Manager Shake Up

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Big Freedia's team continues to struggle at SXSW, one of the biggest music festivals in the world. The Queen of Bounce decides that a personnel change might be in order.

3.title: Bounce University

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Back in New Orleans, the Queen of Bounce and her team prepare for Katy Red's 15th anniversary performance and a lecture at Tulane University. Only problem is that the Shake Team have gone "Hollywood," giving a whole lotta of attitude and little effort.

4.title: No Place Like Home

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: With Vera's health in decline, Freedia focuses on staying in New Orleans so he can work on his new album, get ready for the upcoming Mardi Gras parade and shop for a house that he could share with his mom.

5.title: New Boss of Bounce

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: Freedia's live show hasn't changed in years and his dancers seem uninspired, so the Queen of Bounce hires a fiery creative director to revamp the show and whip the dancers into shape.

6.title: Goodbye Vera

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: Devastated by his mother's passing, Freedia tries to be strong for his family and friends as they rally to give her a big, New Orleans send off with a second line parade.

7.title: Shake Out

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

7.plot: In a clear sign that she has reached the pinnacle of success in New Orleans, Freedia is honored with the Entertainer of the Year award at New Orleans premiere music event, The Big Easy Awards. But there's much to do before the show will be ready for the rest of the world.

8.title: Bounce Goes Hollywood

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

8.plot: Team Freedia is ready to put all their hard work to the test as they prepare to unveil their new live show in LA, but success doesn't come easy as they also have to juggle a music video shoot and promotional events for Freedia's new album release. Will Team Freedia cave under the pressure and demands in LA?

1.title: Just Be Free

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Big Freedia launches her biggest tour ever with a building-shaking, window-breaking show.

2.title: Flash's Dance

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Freedia hits Atlanta for the first major venue of her biggest tour yet, as dancer Flash looks forward to a life-changing reunion with his birth mother.

3.title: Freedia's Twerk on Washington

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Freedia's next tour stop? The nation's capital, Washington D.C. The show is a special tribute for Freedia's late mother Vera's birthday so everything has to be perfect - But will it be?

4.title: The Dirtiest Song Ever Recorded

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Team Freedia hits Denver, Katey Red drops in, and Freedia meets R&B diva Faith Evans. Things take a turn when Freedia gets some upsetting news about her boyfriend.

5.title: Trouble in Paradise

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: While Freedia's in Hawaii for a big show and much-deserved R&R, boyfriend troubles back home threaten to ruin his tropical bliss.

6.title: Big Bad Voodoo Finale

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: After 5 long weeks on the road, Freedia and the team return to New Orleans to end the Just Be Free tour at the Voodoo Music Festival as the Queen Diva makes a life changing decision.

1.title: Freedia Takes Manhattan

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Team Freedia twerks through NYC and gets a shock when she meets with the publishers of her upcoming autobiography, and Skip dreams of bouncing on Broadway.

2.title: Art of the Azz

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Freedia explores new creative frontiers when she invites the people of New Orleans to an open call photo shoot celebrating the art of the Azz and all things Twerk while also trying to work on her relationship with Devon.

3.title: She Wanna Have a Good Time

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Freedia struggles to overcome vocal problems in time to record a new collaboration, while Flash hopes to reunite with his long lost brother and Devon turns to Uncle Percy for advice on life & love.

4.title: Big Freedia's Twerk of Art

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Freedia heads to LA for the all-star opening of her photography exhibit, while her boyfriend Devon plans a surprise for her return. Meanwhile, dancer Flash hopes to become a recording artist.

5.title: Buku or Bust

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: Freedia reunites with her father, and Skip and Flash get one step closer to their as the team rocks Buku Fest.

6.title: Shake, Wiggle, Work

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: As Team Freedia prepares for their European tour they shoot a music video fro Dangerous, and the Queen Diva suffers an injury that could stall her career.

7.title: Ich Liebe Dich

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

7.plot: Team Freedia twerks across the pond to kick-off their European tour in Berlin, Germany where they find unexpected opportunities to expand the brand, and Freedia must make an important decision regarding the team's future.

1.title: One Busy Queen

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

1.plot: Queen Diva returns with bigger goals and a new manager to help make her dreams come true, but tension with Melvin could derail their plans; Flash and Skip form a musical group with DJ Juan; Devon pursues the idea of marrying Freedia.

2.title: Pop Goes the Question

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

2.plot: Freedia prepares for her first major movie role; Devon works up the courage to surprise his Queen with a proposal at her star-studded birthday party.

3.title: OMG It's Beyoncé

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

3.plot: Freedia and Devon can't decide on details for their dream wedding; a phone call from Beyonce; a homeless Flash.

4.title: Get in Formation

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

4.plot: Big Freedia's feature on Beyonce's "Formation" gets the Queen Diva lots of publicity, but a fight with Devon at Mardis Gras garners the wrong kind of attention; Tootie wants to bring back former dancer Steph and reunite the Shake Team.

5.title: Twerkloose

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

5.plot: Freedia courts controversy when a concert in Mississippi gets canceled for excessive twerking; the team prepares to debut new music from the Queen Diva's upcoming album; Tootie gives back to the community.

6.title: It's Soul Food

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

6.plot: A federal indictment rocks Freedia as she tries to expand her brand by launching Big Freedia's Soul Food; Flash seeks to connect with his long-lost family.

7.title: Diva's Day in Court

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

7.plot: Freedia has her day in court and faces a media circus; Flash heads to Michigan to meet his great grandmother and learn about his past.

8.title: Right to Twerk

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

8.plot: Freedia's previously banned Mississippi performance is rescheduled, the team decides to commemorate the show by filming a music video for her new single I Heard.Tootie surprises the girl she's mentoring with an opportunity at NOLA Fashion Week.

9.title: Twerkout

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

9.plot: Freedia expands her brand to the digital world when she produces a Bounce-based exercise app. When the team builds a home for a local family through Habitat for Humanity, Tootie channels her inner construction worker.

10.title: Soul Food Pop-up

episode of.title: Big Freedia: Queen of Bounce (TV Series 2013– )

10.plot: With her sentencing hearing looming and her future uncertain, Freedia prepares to launch a pop-up restaurant. And after a tumultuous engagement, Freedia and Devon make a tough decision about their relationship.

imdb.plot outline: This show follows Big Freedia (born Frederick Ross) on her journey toward superstardom in the mainstream media. As the undisputed ambassador of the energetic, New Orleans-based Bounce movement, Big Freedia is never afraid to twerk, wiggle, and shake her way to self-confidence, and is encouraging her fans to do the same.
